#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/index.rst:5
msgid "GDAL algorithm provider"
msgstr "Dobavljač GDAL algoritma"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/index.rst:7
msgid ""
"`GDAL <https://gdal.org/en/latest>`_ (Geospatial Data Abstraction Library) "
"is a translator library for raster and vector geospatial data formats. "
"Algorithms in the Processing Framework are derived from the `GDAL raster "
"programs <https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/index.html#raster-programs>`_ "
"and `GDAL vector programs "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/index.html#vector-programs>`_."
msgstr ""
"`GDAL <https://gdal.org/en/latest>`_ (Biblioteka za apstrakciju "
"geoprostornih podataka) je biblioteka za prevod rasterskih i vektorskih "
"geoprostornih formata podataka. Algoritmi u okviru za obradu podataka su "
"izvedeni iz `GDAL rasterskih programa "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/index.html#raster-programs>`_ i `GDAL "
"vektorskih programa <https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/index.html#vector-"
"programs>`_."
